(39, 'R7N695', 'Watan waalon watan na bech dena\r\nYeh dharti yeh gagan na bech dena\r\nShaheedon ne jaan di hai watan ke vaaste\r\nShaheedon ke kafan na bech dena', 'Daljeet Singh', 'daljeet.working@gmail.com', '127.0.0.1', 1, '2013-11-23 20:09:08', '2013-11-23 20:09:08'),
(40, 'T7N695', '"Blood which is wasted in a college/street fights or fight for a girl has no value. But a single drop of blood becomes priceless when it serves the Nation"', 'Daljeet Singh', 'daljeet.working@gmail.com', '127.0.0.1', 1, '2013-11-23 20:09:29', '2013-11-23 20:09:29'),
(41, 'Y7N695', '"I am a man and all that affects mankind concerns me"\r\n- Bhagat Singh (Page 43 of Jail notebook)', 'Daljeet Singh', 'daljeet.working@gmail.com', '127.0.0.1', 1, '2013-11-23 20:10:06', '2013-11-23 20:10:06'),
